Tyrael started to get on the Night Star. He stood in the doorway, and 
received a signal that all the pods were inside. He called for the 
soldiers not already aboard.

Tyrael: Naga, Talon, we will wait for both of you on the bridge of the 
ship. Shadow Star, tell me when all systems are operational please.

He walks slowly to the bridge. Soon, he would have to make his report 
to the High Council before going. Upon their shoulder rested the very 
future of the Tripredacus... Life really was a bitch...
